title: Submit
---

<h2>Send your submissions to <a href="mailto:press@grinnell.edu">press@grinnell.edu</a> via email or WeTransfer. The deadline for Fall 2019 is October 19.</h2>

<p>Send either all the work want published, or a proposal including a sample of the work. This typically means 8-10 photos/artworks/poems, or 1-2 short stories/chapters.</p>

